{"title":"表格和表单","date":"2020-11-06T07:01:35.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年11月6日","L":"2020/11/06","MM-DD":"11-06"},"link":"posts/80afbc07","comments":true,"tags":["HTML5+CSS3"],"categories":["网页设计"],"updated":"2020-11-15T09:53:42.843Z","content":"<h1 id=\"表格\">表格<a href=\"#表格\" title=\"表格\"></a></h1><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201106150910.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><h2 id=\"lttablegt属性\"><code>&lt;table&gt;</code>属性<a href=\"#lttablegt属性\" title=\"&lt;table&gt;属性\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201106151158.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><blockquote>\n<p><code>&lt;table&gt;</code>标签属性在实体表格中的表现如下图所示：</p>\n</blockquote>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201106151416.png\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201106151757.png\" style=\"zoom:50%;\" /><h2 id=\"lttrgt标签的属性\"><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签的属性<a href=\"#lttrgt标签的属性\" title=\"&lt;tr&gt;标签的属性\"></a></h2><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>属性</strong></th><th><strong>描述</strong></th><th><strong>常用属性值</strong></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>height</strong></td><td>设置行高度</td><td>像素值</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>align</strong></td><td>设置一行内容的水平对齐方式</td><td>left、center、right</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>valign</strong></td><td>设置一行内容的垂直对齐方式</td><td>top、middle、bottom</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>bgcolor</strong></td><td>设置行背景颜色</td><td>预定义的颜色值、十六进制#RGB、rgb(r,g,b)</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>background</strong></td><td>设置行背景图像</td><td>url地址</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><blockquote>\n<p>注意</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol><li><p><code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签无宽度属性width，其宽度取决于表格标签<code>&lt;table&gt;</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>对<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签应用<code>valign</code>属性，用于设置<strong>一行内容的垂直对齐方式</strong>。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>虽然可以对<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签应用background属性，但是在<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>标签中此属性兼容问题严重。</p>\n</li>\n</ol><h2 id=\"lttdgt标签的属性\"><code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签的属性<a href=\"#lttdgt标签的属性\" title=\"&lt;td&gt;标签的属性\"></a></h2><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>属性名</strong></th><th><strong>含义</strong></th><th><strong>常用属性值</strong></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>width</strong></td><td>设置单元格的宽度</td><td>像素值</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>height</strong></td><td>设置单元格的高度</td><td>像素值</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>align</strong></td><td>设置单元格内容的水平对齐方式</td><td>left、center、right</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>valign</strong></td><td>设置单元格内容的垂直对齐方式</td><td>top、middle、bottom</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>bgcolor</strong></td><td>设置单元格的背景颜色</td><td>预定义的颜色值、十六进制#RGB、rgb(r,g,b)</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>background</strong></td><td>设置单元格的背景图像</td><td>url地址</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>colspan</strong></td><td>设置单元格横跨的列数（用于合并水平方向的单元格）</td><td>正整数</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>rowspan</strong></td><td>设置单元格竖跨的行数（用于合并竖直方向的单元格）</td><td>正整数</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><blockquote>\n<p>注意</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol><li><p>在<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签的属性中，重点掌握colspan和rolspan，其他的属性了解即可，不建议使用，均可用CSS样式属性替代。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>当对某一个<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签应用width属性设置宽度时，该列中的所有单元格均会以设置的宽度显示。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>当对某一个<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签应用height属性设置高度时，该行中的所有单元格均会以设置的高度显示。</p>\n</li>\n</ol><h2 id=\"ltthgt表头标签\"><code>&lt;th&gt;</code>表头标签<a href=\"#ltthgt表头标签\" title=\"&lt;th&gt;表头标签\"></a></h2><ul><li>默认加粗居中显示</li>\n</ul><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201109083903.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><h1 id=\"css控制表格样式\">CSS控制表格样式<a href=\"#css控制表格样式\" title=\"CSS控制表格样式\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"表格边框\">表格边框<a href=\"#表格边框\" title=\"表格边框\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201109085536.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><blockquote>\n<p>注意</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ol><li><p><code>border-collapse</code>属性的属性值除了<code>collapse</code>（合并）之外，还可以为<code>separate</code>（分离），默认为<code>separate</code>。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>当表格的<code>border-collapse</code>属性设置为<code>collapse</code>时， HTML中设置的<code>cellspacing</code>属性值无效。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>行标签<code>&lt;tr&gt;</code>无<code>border</code>样式属性，本书不再做具体的演示，初学者可以自己测试加深理解。</p>\n</li>\n</ol><h2 id=\"单元格边距\">单元格边距<a href=\"#单元格边距\" title=\"单元格边距\"></a></h2><p>设置<strong>单元格内容</strong>与<strong>边框</strong>之间的距离，可以对<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>标签应用内边距样式属性padding，或对<code>&lt;table&gt;</code>标签应用HTML标签属性<code>cellpadding</code>。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">th</span>,<span class=\"selector-tag\">td</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">border</span>:<span class=\"number\">1px</span> solid <span class=\"number\">#30F</span>;     <span class=\"comment\">/*为单元格单独设置边框*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">padding</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;              <span class=\"comment\">/*为单元格内容与边框设置20px的内边距*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"attribute\">margin</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;     <span class=\"comment\">/*为单元格与单元格边框之间设置20px的外边距*/</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"> &#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"单元格的宽高\">单元格的宽高<a href=\"#单元格的宽高\" title=\"单元格的宽高\"></a></h2><p>对单元格标签<code>&lt;td&gt;</code>应用width和height属性，可以控制单元格<strong>宽度和高度</strong>。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">td</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">width</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"attribute\">Height</span>:<span class=\"number\">20px</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote>\n<p>对同一行中的单元格定义不同的高度，或对同一列中的单元格定义不同的宽度时，最终的宽度或高度<strong>将取其中的较大者</strong>。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"表单\">表单<a href=\"#表单\" title=\"表单\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"创建\">创建<a href=\"#创建\" title=\"创建\"></a></h2><p><code>&lt;form&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</code>标签用来创建表单。</p>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201109090030.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"url地址\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交方式\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"表单名称\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t各种表单控件</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><code>&lt;form&gt;</code>与<code>&lt;/form&gt;</code>之间的表单控件是由用户自定义的，action、method和name为表单标签<code>&lt;form&gt;</code>的常用属性。</p>\n<h2 id=\"表单控件\">表单控件<a href=\"#表单控件\" title=\"表单控件\"></a></h2><h3 id=\"input控件\">input控件<a href=\"#input控件\" title=\"input控件\"></a></h3><ul><li><p><code>&lt;input /&gt;</code>元素是表单中最常见的元素，网页中常见的<strong>单行文本框</strong>、<strong>单选按钮</strong>、<strong>复选框</strong>等都是通过它定义的。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"控件类型\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>\n<li><p><code>&lt;input /&gt;</code>标签为单标签，<code>type</code>属性为其最基本的属性，其取值有多种，用于指定不同的控件类型。</p>\n</li>\n</ul><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201109090453.png\" style=\"zoom:80%;\" /><p><code>hidden</code>对于用户是不可见的，通常用于后台的程序</p>\n<form action=\"#\" method=\"get\">\n请输入邮政编码：<input type=\"text\" name=\"code\" pattern=\"[0-9]{6}\" placeholder=\"请输入6位数的邮政编码\" />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\"/>\n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入邮政编码：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"code\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"[0-9]&#123;6&#125;\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">placeholder</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"请输入6位数的邮政编码\"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"textarea控件\">textarea控件<a href=\"#textarea控件\" title=\"textarea控件\"></a></h3><textarea cols=\"每行中的字符数\" rows=\"显示的行数\">\n    文本内容\n</textarea><ul><li><p><code>cols</code>和<code>rows</code>为<code>&lt;textarea&gt;</code>标记的必须属性</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>cols</code>用来定义多行文本输入框<strong>每行中的字符数</strong></p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>rows</code>用来定义多行文本输入框显示的<strong>行数</strong>，取值均为<strong>正整数</strong>。</p>\n</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">textarea</span> <span class=\"attr\">cols</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"每行中的字符数\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">rows</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"显示的行数\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t文本内容</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">textarea</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th><strong>属性</strong></th><th><strong>属性值</strong></th><th><strong>描述</strong></th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>name</strong></td><td>由用户自定义</td><td>控件的名称</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>readonly</strong></td><td>readonly</td><td>该控件内容为只读（不能编辑修改）</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>disabled</strong></td><td>disabled</td><td>第一次加载页面时禁用该控件（显示为灰色）</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><h3 id=\"select控件\">select控件<a href=\"#select控件\" title=\"select控件\"></a></h3><select>\n        <option>选项1</option>\n        <option>选项2</option>\n        <option>选项3</option>\n       ...\n</select><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>选项1<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>选项2<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>选项3<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">       ...</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote>\n<p><code>&lt;select&gt;</code>和<code>&lt;option&gt;</code>标签属性</p>\n</blockquote>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201110102646.png\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" /><form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n城区：<br />\n    <select>\n        <optgroup label=\"北京\">\n            <option>东城区</option>\n            <option>西城区</option>\n            <option>朝阳区</option>\n            <option>海淀区</option>\n        </optgroup>\n        <optgroup label=\"上海\">\n            <option>浦东新区</option>\n            <option>徐汇区</option>\n            <option>虹口区</option>\n        </optgroup>\n    </select>\n</form>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"post\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">城区：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">optgroup</span> <span class=\"attr\">label</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"北京\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>东城区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>西城区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>朝阳区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>海淀区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">optgroup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">optgroup</span> <span class=\"attr\">label</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"上海\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>浦东新区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>徐汇区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>虹口区<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">optgroup</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h1 id=\"html5表单新属性\">HTML5表单新属性<a href=\"#html5表单新属性\" title=\"HTML5表单新属性\"></a></h1><h2 id=\"form属性\">form属性<a href=\"#form属性\" title=\"form属性\"></a></h2><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201110103124.png\" style=\"zoom:67%;\" /><h3 id=\"autocomplete\">autocomplete<a href=\"#autocomplete\" title=\"autocomplete\"></a></h3><ul><li>将表单控件输入的内容记录下来，下次输入，显示在下拉列表里</li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"formBox\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">autocomplete</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"on\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"novalidate\">novalidate<a href=\"#novalidate\" title=\"novalidate\"></a></h3><p><code>&lt;form&gt;</code>标签内的所有表单控件不被验证</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"form_action.asp\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">novalidate</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"novalidate\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"datalist表单控件--既可选择也可填写\">datalist表单控件  (既可选择也可填写)<a href=\"#datalist表单控件--既可选择也可填写\" title=\"datalist表单控件  (既可选择也可填写)\"></a></h2><ul><li><p>网页中的列表通过<code>datalist</code>内的<code>option</code>进行创建。如果用户不希望从列表中选择某项，也可以自行输入其他内容。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p><code>datalist</code>控件通常与<code>input</code>控件配合使用，来定义<code>input</code>的取值。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>在使用<code>&lt;datalist&gt;</code>控件时，需要通过<code>id</code>属性为其指定一个唯一的标识，然后为<code>input</code>控件指定<code>list</code>属性，将该属性值设置为<code>datalist</code>对应的id属性值即可。</p>\n</li>\n</ul><form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n请输入用户名：<input type=\"text\" list=\"namelist\"/>\n<datalist id=\"namelist\">\n    <option>admin</option>\n    <option>lucy</option>\n    <option>lily</option>\n</datalist>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\" />        \n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"post\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入用户名：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">list</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"namelist\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">datalist</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"namelist\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>admin<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>lucy<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span>lily<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">datalist</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span> /&gt;</span>\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"全新的input\">全新的input<a href=\"#全新的input\" title=\"全新的input\"></a></h2><p>请输入您的邮箱：<input type=\"email\" name=\"formmail\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请输入您的邮箱：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"email\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"formmail\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>请输入个人网址：<input type=\"url\" name=\"user_url\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请输入个人网址：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"url\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_url\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>请输入电话号码：<input type=\"tel\" name=\"telphone\" pattern=\"^\\d{11}$\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请输入电话号码：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"tel\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"telphone\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"^\\d&#123;11&#125;$\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>输入搜索关键词：<input type=\"search\" name=\"searchinfo\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">输入搜索关键词：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"search\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"searchinfo\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>请选取一种颜色：<input type=\"color\" name=\"color1\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请选取一种颜色：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"color\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"color1\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span id=\"two\"></span></p>\n<p>请输入数值：<input type=\"number\" name=\"number1\" value=\"1\" min=\"1\" max=\"20\" step=\"4\"/></p>\n<p><a href=\"#one\"><code>value</code>: 输入框的默认值 <code>max</code> ：输入框接受的最大值 <code>min</code>： 最小值   <code>step</code>: 输入域合法的间隔（单击按钮跳动的±4，默认1)</a></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">请输入数值：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"number\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"number1\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"1\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">min</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"1\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">max</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"20\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">step</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"4\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>时间日期 : <input type=\"date\"/><br>月、年：<input type=\"month\"/><br>周、年：<input type=\"week\"/><br>小时分钟：<input type=\"time\"/><br>时间、日、月、年：<input type=\"datetime\"/><br>时间、日月年：<input type=\"datetime-local\"/></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"date\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"month\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"week\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"time\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"datetime\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"datetime-local\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"autofocus属性-自动获取该焦点\">autofocus属性 自动获取该焦点<a href=\"#autofocus属性-自动获取该焦点\" title=\"autofocus属性 自动获取该焦点\"></a></h3><ul><li>页面加载完毕后会<strong>自动获取该焦点</strong></li>\n</ul><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入搜索关键词：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_name\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">autocomplete</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"off\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">autofocus</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"true\"</span>/&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"form属性-子元素在任意位置\">form属性 子元素在任意位置<a href=\"#form属性-子元素在任意位置\" title=\"form属性 子元素在任意位置\"></a></h3><p>可以把表单内的子元素写在页面中的任一位置，只需为这个元素指定<strong><code>form</code>属性</strong>并设置属性值为该表单的id即可</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>例</p>\n</blockquote>\n<form action=\"#\" method=\"get\" id=\"user_form\">\n请输入您的姓名：<input type=\"text\" name=\"first_name\"/>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\" />    \n</form>\n<p>下面的输入框在form元素外，但因为指定了form属性为表单的id，所以该输入框仍然属于表单的一部分。</p>\n请输入您的昵称：<input type=\"text\" name=\"last_name\" form=\"user_form\"/><br/><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_form\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入您的姓名：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"first_name\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span> /&gt;</span>\t</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span>下面的输入框在form元素外，但因为指定了form属性为表单的id，所以该输入框仍然属于表单的一部分。<span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入您的昵称：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"last_name\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">form</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_form\"</span>/&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"list属性\">list属性<a href=\"#list属性\" title=\"list属性\"></a></h3><p>指定输入框所绑定的<code>datalist</code>元素，其值是某个<code>datalist</code>元素的<code>id</code>。</p>\n<form action=\"#\" method=\"get\">\n请输入网址：<input type=\"url\" list=\"url_list\" name=\"weburl\"/>\n<datalist id=\"url_list\">\n    <option label=\"新浪\" value=\"http://www.sina.com.cn\"></option>\n    <option label=\"搜狐\" value=\"http://www.sohu.com\"></option>\n    <option label=\"IT\" value=\"http://www.it.cn/\"></option>\n</datalist>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\"/>\n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入网址：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"url\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">list</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"url_list\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"weburl\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">datalist</span> <span class=\"attr\">id</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"url_list\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span> <span class=\"attr\">label</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"新浪\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"http://www.sina.com.cn\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span> <span class=\"attr\">label</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"搜狐\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"http://www.sohu.com\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">option</span> <span class=\"attr\">label</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"IT\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"http://www.it.cn/\"</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">datalist</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"multiple属性-选择多个值\">multiple属性 <strong>选择多个值</strong><a href=\"#multiple属性-选择多个值\" title=\"multiple属性 选择多个值\"></a></h3><p>输入框可以<strong>选择多个值</strong>，该属性适用于<code>email</code>和<code>file</code>类型的<code>input</code>元素。</p>\n<form action=\"#\" method=\"get\">\n电子邮箱：<input type=\"email\" name=\"myemail\" multiple/>&nbsp;&nbsp;（如果电子邮箱有多个，请使用逗号分隔）<br/><br/>\n上传照片：<input type=\"file\" name=\"selfile\" multiple/><br/><br/>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\"/>\n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">电子邮箱：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"email\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"myemail\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">multiple</span>/&gt;</span><span class=\"symbol\">&amp;nbsp;</span><span class=\"symbol\">&amp;nbsp;</span>（如果电子邮箱有多个，请使用逗号分隔）<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">上传照片：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"file\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"selfile\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">multiple</span>/&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><span id=\"one\"></span></p>\n<h3 id=\"min、max和step属性\">min、max和step属性<a href=\"#min、max和step属性\" title=\"min、max和step属性\"></a></h3><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/dxsummer/cdn/img/html/20201115172927.png\" style=\"zoom: 67%;\" /><ul><li><a href=\"#two\">min、max和step属性用于为包含数字或日期的input输入类型规定限值</a></li>\n<li>适用于date、pickers、number和range标签</li>\n</ul><h3 id=\"pattern属性-正则表达式\">pattern属性 正则表达式<a href=\"#pattern属性-正则表达式\" title=\"pattern属性 正则表达式\"></a></h3><ul><li>验证<code>input</code>类型输入框中，用户输入的内容是否与所定义的正则表达式相匹配</li>\n<li>适用于的类型是：text、search、url、tel、email和password的<code>&lt;input/&gt;</code>标签。</li>\n</ul><p><font color=\"red\" size=\"5px\"><strong>常用的正则表达式和说明</strong></font></p>\n<div class=\"φcz\"><div class=\"φdb\"><table><thead><tr>\n<th>正则表达式</th><th>说明</th></tr>\n</thead><tbody><tr>\n<td>^[0-9]*$</td><td>数字</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^\\d{n}$</td><td>n位的数字</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^\\d{n,}$</td><td>至少n位的数字</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^\\d{m,n}$</td><td>m-n位的数字</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^(0|[1-9][0-9]*)$</td><td>零和非零开头的数字</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^([1-9][0-9]*)+(.[0-9]{1,2})?$</td><td>非零开头的最多带两位小数的数字</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^(-|+)?\\d+(.\\d+)?$</td><td>正数、负数、和小数</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^\\d+$ 或 ^[1-9]\\d*|0$</td><td>非负整数</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^-[1-9]\\d*|0$ 或 ^((-\\d+)|(0+))$</td><td>非正整数</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^[\\u4e00-\\u9fa5]{0,}$</td><td>汉字</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^[A-Za-z0-9]+$ 或 ^[A-Za-z0-9]{4,40}$</td><td>英文和数字</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^[A-Za-z]+$</td><td>由26个英文字母组成的字符串</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^[A-Za-z0-9]+$</td><td>由数字和26个英文字母组成的字符串</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^\\w+$ 或 ^\\w{3,20}$</td><td>由数字、26个英文字母或者下划线组成的字符串</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^[\\u4E00-\\u9FA5A-Za-z0-9_]+$</td><td>中文、英文、数字包括下划线</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^\\w+([-+.]\\w+)<em>@\\w+([-.]\\w+)*.\\w+([-.]\\w+)</em>$</td><td>Email地址</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>[a-zA-z]+://[^\\s]* 或 ^http://([\\w-]+.)+[\\w-]+(/[\\w-./?%&amp;=]*)?$</td><td>URL地址</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^\\d{15}|\\d{18}$</td><td>身份证号(15位、18位数字)</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^([0-9]){7,18}(x|X)?$ 或 ^\\d{8,18}|[0-9x]{8,18}|[0-9X]{8,18}?$</td><td>以数字、字母x结尾的短身份证号码</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]{4,15}$</td><td>帐号是否合法(字母开头，允许5-16字节，允许字母数字下划线)</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<td>^[a-zA-Z]\\w{5,17}$</td><td>密码(以字母开头，长度在6~18之间，只能包含字母、数字和下划线)</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></div></div><blockquote>\n<p>eg</p>\n</blockquote>\n<form action=\"#\" method=\"get\">\n账&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;号：<input type=\"text\" name=\"username\" pattern=\"^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]{4,15}$\" />（以字母开头，允许5-16字节，允许字母数字下划线）<br/>\n密&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;码：<input type=\"password\" name=\"pwd\" pattern=\"^[a-zA-Z]\\w{5,17}$\" />（以字母开头，长度在6~18之间，只能包含字母、数字和下划线）<br/>\n身份证号：<input type=\"text\" name=\"mycard\" pattern=\"^\\d{15}|\\d{18}$\" />（15位、18位数字）<br/>\nEmail地址：<input type=\"email\" name=\"myemail\" pattern=\"^\\w+([-+.]\\w+)*@\\w+([-.]\\w+)*\\.\\w+([-.]\\w+)*$\"/>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\"/>\n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    账号：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"username\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9_]&#123;4,15&#125;$\"</span> /&gt;</span>（以字母开头，允许5-16字节，允许字母数字下划线）<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    密码：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"password\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"pwd\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"^[a-zA-Z]\\w&#123;5,17&#125;$\"</span> /&gt;</span>（以字母开头，长度在6~18之间，只能包含字母、数字和下划线）<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t身份证号：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"mycard\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"^\\d&#123;15&#125;|\\d&#123;18&#125;$\"</span> /&gt;</span>（15位、18位数字）<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">br</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    Email地址：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"email\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"myemail\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"^\\w+([-+.]\\w+)*@\\w+([-.]\\w+)*\\.\\w+([-.]\\w+)*$\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"placeholder属性-提示信息\">placeholder属性 提示信息<a href=\"#placeholder属性-提示信息\" title=\"placeholder属性 提示信息\"></a></h3><ul><li>为<code>input</code>类型的输入框提供相关提示信息，以描述输入框期待用户输入何种内容。</li>\n</ul><form action=\"#\" method=\"get\">\n请输入邮政编码：<input type=\"text\" name=\"code\" pattern=\"[0-9]{6}\" placeholder=\"请输入6位数的邮政编码\" />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\"/>\n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入邮政编码：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"code\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">pattern</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"[0-9]&#123;6&#125;\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">placeholder</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"请输入6位数的邮政编码\"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id=\"required属性-内容不能为空\">required属性 内容不能为空<a href=\"#required属性-内容不能为空\" title=\"required属性 内容不能为空\"></a></h3><ul><li>规定输入框填写的内容不能为空，否则不允许用户提交表单。</li>\n</ul><form action=\"#\" method=\"get\">\n请输入姓名：<input type=\"text\" name=\"user_name\" required=\"required\"/>\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"提交\"/>\n</form><figure class=\"highlight html\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">form</span> <span class=\"attr\">action</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"#\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">method</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"get\"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">请输入姓名：<span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"text\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">name</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"user_name\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">required</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"required\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;<span class=\"name\">input</span> <span class=\"attr\">type</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"submit\"</span> <span class=\"attr\">value</span>=<span class=\"string\">\"提交\"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"name\">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>","prev":{"title":"树和二叉树","link":"posts/ec2e91f9"},"next":{"title":"导航栏","link":"posts/25281569"},"plink":"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/80afbc07/","toc":[{"id":"表格","title":"表格","index":"1","children":[{"id":"lttablegt属性","title":"&lt;table&gt;属性","index":"1.1"},{"id":"lttrgt标签的属性","title":"&lt;tr&gt;标签的属性","index":"1.2"},{"id":"lttdgt标签的属性","title":"&lt;td&gt;标签的属性","index":"1.3"},{"id":"ltthgt表头标签","title":"&lt;th&gt;表头标签","index":"1.4"}]},{"id":"css控制表格样式","title":"CSS控制表格样式","index":"2","children":[{"id":"表格边框","title":"表格边框","index":"2.1"},{"id":"单元格边距","title":"单元格边距","index":"2.2"},{"id":"单元格的宽高","title":"单元格的宽高","index":"2.3"}]},{"id":"表单","title":"表单","index":"3","children":[{"id":"创建","title":"创建","index":"3.1"},{"id":"表单控件","title":"表单控件","index":"3.2","children":[{"id":"input控件","title":"input控件","index":"3.2.1"},{"id":"textarea控件","title":"textarea控件","index":"3.2.2"},{"id":"select控件","title":"select控件","index":"3.2.3"}]}]},{"id":"html5表单新属性","title":"HTML5表单新属性","index":"4","children":[{"id":"form属性","title":"form属性","index":"4.1","children":[{"id":"autocomplete","title":"autocomplete","index":"4.1.1"},{"id":"novalidate","title":"novalidate","index":"4.1.2"}]},{"id":"datalist表单控件--既可选择也可填写","title":"datalist表单控件  (既可选择也可填写)","index":"4.2"},{"id":"全新的input","title":"全新的input","index":"4.3","children":[{"id":"autofocus属性-自动获取该焦点","title":"autofocus属性 自动获取该焦点","index":"4.3.1"},{"id":"form属性-子元素在任意位置","title":"form属性 子元素在任意位置","index":"4.3.2"},{"id":"list属性","title":"list属性","index":"4.3.3"},{"id":"multiple属性-选择多个值","title":"multiple属性 选择多个值","index":"4.3.4"},{"id":"min、max和step属性","title":"min、max和step属性","index":"4.3.5"},{"id":"pattern属性-正则表达式","title":"pattern属性 正则表达式","index":"4.3.6"},{"id":"placeholder属性-提示信息","title":"placeholder属性 提示信息","index":"4.3.7"},{"id":"required属性-内容不能为空","title":"required属性 内容不能为空","index":"4.3.8"}]}]}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"DxSummer","link":"<a href=\"https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/80afbc07/\" title=\"表格和表单\">https://dxsummer.gitee.io/posts/80afbc07/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\\\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\\\" rel=\\\"external nofollow\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)","published":"2020年11月6日","updated":"2020年11月15日"}}